ğŸš€ Project Name: Samyukt

A unified platform for citizens to report civic issues and for authorities to resolve them efficiently.

ğŸ¯ Core Idea (Very Clean & Interview-Ready)

Samyukt ek centralized complaint & issue tracking system hai jisme:

Citizens apne area ki problems report karte hain
(e.g., garbage, street-light failure, water leakage, broken roads, electricity issues, village problems, etc.)

Resolvers (City departments / village panchayat / authorities) un complaints ko receive karte hain

24 hours ke andar unko status update dena hota hai

Resolve hone ke baad image + closing note ke saath problem close karte hain

System ka goal: Cities aur villages dono ke real problems ko one unified platform par solve karna.

Iska naam Samyukt isliye â€” kyunki system citizens + authorities + issues sab ko together connect karta hai.

