resolvedAt  
timestamps  

ğŸ”„ System Flow (Easy to Explain)
Citizen â†’ Complaint Create â†’ Resolver Assigned â†’ Update in 24hrs â†’ Resolve â†’ Notify back

User logs in

Creates complaint

System auto-assigns to department (based on category)

Resolver sees it on dashboard

Updates ETA within 24 hrs

Fixes issue & uploads resolution image

Complaint becomes â€œResolvedâ€

User notified

User can track entire lifecycle anytime